			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I am not sure if this has been addressed else where but At 64 now my warder "Dozer" is just really to big (even with Tiny companion) and I have found that if I am with a group doing a Ldon he can get in the way he is hard to manuver in the dungeon and overall just plain in the way.
<br />

<br />
Now I have sent this feedback several times but figure the more we ask for it the better.
<br />

