<br />

<br />
Slot 	Description
<br />
4: 	Increase STR by 50
<br />
5: 	Increase DEX by 55
<br />
6: 	Increase STA by 45
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Khura's Focusing</span>
<br />

<br />
Slot 	Description
<br />
1: 	Increase Max Hitpoints by 430 (L60) to 445 (L65)
<br />
2: 	Increase HP when cast by 430 (L60) to 445 (L65)
<br />
4: 	Increase STR by 67
<br />
5: 	Increase DEX by 60
<br />
6: 	Stacking: Overwrite existing spell if slot 1 is effect 'STR' and &lt; 67
<br />
7: 	Stacking: Overwrite existing spell if slot 1 is effect 'DEX' and &lt; 60
<br />
8: 	Stacking: Block new spell if slot 1 is effect 'STR' and &lt; 1067
<br />
9: 	Stacking: Block new spell if slot 1 is effect 'DEX' and &lt; 1060
<br />
10: 	Stacking: Overwrite existing spell if slot 1 is effect 'Max Hitpoints' and &lt; 1100</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
