I posted parses of numerous buff setups and it showed the only gain with the 64 warder was with dexterity once you have arag's and rellic on it.  Adding a str buff or IoS made no difference in average hit, dps, or proc rate.  So the 3 main buffs needed would be Arag's, Rellic, Dexterity.  Anything else is a waste of mana unless it's Kragg or Spiritual Brawn for additional hp.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=362635" target="_blank" class="postlink">Derrict</a> - 65 rogue| <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=752370" target="_blank" class="postlink">Ferome</a> - 65 beastlord
